#: of spack.hooks.absolutify_elf_sonames.is_shared_library_elf:1
msgid ""
"Return true if filepath is most a shared library. Our definition of a shared "
"library for ELF requires: 1. a dynamic section, 2. a soname OR lack of "
"interpreter. The problem is that PIE objects (default on Ubuntu) are ET_DYN "
"too, and not all shared libraries have a soname... no interpreter is "
"typically the best indicator then."
msgstr ""

